<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>.stepper {
  padding-top: 30px;
  padding-bottom: 30px;
}
.stepper .step {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 32px;
}
.stepper .step > div:last-child {
  margin-left: 32px;
  padding-left: 16px;
}
.stepper .step .step-heading {
  position: static;
  height: 33px;
  color: #fff;
  padding-bottom: 50px;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.stepper .step .step-heading .circle {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  line-height: 32px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  position: relative;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  float: left;
}
.stepper .step .step-heading .title {
  line-height: 32px;
  padding-left: 15px;
  float: left;
}
.stepper .step .body {
  padding-bottom: 30px;
}
.stepper .step .line {
  position: absolute;
  border-left: 1px solid #fff;
  left: 16px;
  bottom: 0px;
  top: 32px;
}
.stepper .step .btn {
  color: #fff !important;
}
</css><name>jiraStepperCss</name><sys_class_name>sp_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>douglas.schamberg</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-02-06 20:37:37</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>false</sys_customer_update><sys_id>8736913ddb7ec410f2551329689619d4</sys_id><sys_mod_count>2</sys_mod_count><sys_name>jiraStepperCss</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Jira Integration" source="x_momo_jira_integr">ec964aa3dbd2c810f25513296896194c</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Jira Integration">ec964aa3dbd2c810f25513296896194c</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_css_8736913ddb7ec410f2551329689619d4</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>douglas.schamberg@movement.com</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-02-06 20:42:28</sys_updated_on></sp_css></record_update>
